txt.en: The Ghâsh-hai are led by the vicious Orc-commander Yûl, and his defeat would be a serious blow to the organization of the principal enemy threat in the Flaming Deeps.

The Ghâsh-hai are led by the vicious Orc-commander Yûl, and his defeat would be a serious blow to the organization of the principal enemy threat in the Flaming Deeps.\n\nYou should seek Yûl and defeat him; such a blow would break the spirit of the Orcs.
Yûl can be found on the highest floor of Hurmulkezer in the south-eastern Flaming Deeps, south of Durin's Court.\n\nYou should find and defeat Yûl.
You have defeated Yûl, the leader of the Ghâsh-hai forces in Hurmulkezer.\n\nWhile many Orcs still remain, they will founder without a leader.
